Avocado rice chickpea salad Chickpeas, also known as garbanzo beans are a healthy meal option packed with folate, magnesium, potassium and iron. They also have a good measure of vitamin A, E and C which helps your brain and nervous system run smoothly. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Combine avocado, chickpeas and shallot in a bowl. Step 2 Mix up spices and sprinkle them over salad ingredients while adding in a squeeze of lime juice, mango and beetroot then toss to combine. Step 3 Add in the chicken and rice then combine. Serve immediately and top with cilantro and a glass of wine or preferred beverage. 